<item>
            <title>[PIG-2998] Fix TestScriptLanguage and TestMacroExpansion</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2998</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a regression from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2931&quot; title=&quot;$ signs in the replacement string make parameter substitution fail&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-2931&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-2931&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I made changes so that $ signs in a replacement string get escaped by PreprocessorContext. But they shouldn&apos;t be escaped if they&apos;re already escaped.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In particular, TestScriptLanguage#bindLocalVariableTest2 is failing in trunk because $ signs are escaped by Pig#bind() and then escaped again by PreprocessorContext.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
