                            <comment id="13482059" author="cheolsoo" created="Tue, 23 Oct 2012 03:29:27 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached is a patch that fixes the failing test.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I changed replaceAll() as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
val = val.replaceAll(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;(?&amp;lt;!\\\\)\\$&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;\\\\\\$&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So only $ signs that are not already escaped get escaped now.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Testing done:&lt;br/&gt;
ant test-commit&lt;br/&gt;
ant test -Dtestcase=TestScriptLanange&lt;br/&gt;
ant test -Dtestcase=TestParamSubPreproc&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
